snippet.title: Johnny Depp SPEAKS On His Major Win Against Amber Heard In Defamation Case!!!
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp SPEAKS On His Major Win Against Amber Heard In Defamation Case!!!
Over the past year Johnny Depp and Amber Heard's relationship has been plastered across the headlines. The details of their life together were revealed when a British newspaper branded the Pirates of the Caribbean star a "w-b", claims which he disputed. Johnny Depp does not seem to be stopping any time soon when it comes to finding any evidence that will support him in his libel case against his ex wife Amber Heard. Everyone is well aware of the fact that the two got a divorce, but it is clear that this has not been one that ended smoothly.
